{
  "stem": "18450.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 16.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And during the period, you traded for food and other things.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then when the Russians came in, it was bad, but not life-threatening.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were still in the-- in the village.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then they said that the Russian troops are coming.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Well, you couldn't go out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They told you to stay in the-- in the houses.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Russians.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they brought a lot of-- nothing happened really too extreme, they should kill us or no.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Nothing happened.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they tried to tell you that things are going to be fine and that the Germans wouldn't come anymore here.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But-- and this ended.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I mean, politics, the Russians didn't like to discuss politics.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was part of their business.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yeah, yeah.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Nothing.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They just went, not knowing where they go.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But they just left, you know, kept them here.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they thought they most safe here, which a lot of them went back because no work, and no food, whatever they they took for them.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was tough, very rough for them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They used to come.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Nobody really occupied our house, no.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But they had-- it was a few hundred.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We had a big, big house, with apartments all around.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My mother, me, and two brothers and I.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My grandmother lived in the same house, but she had your own bedrooms and-- and kitchen.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the other was rented to our tailor.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't remember even his name.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He had three rooms.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And there was another two rooms rented to somebody next door, which was a rich man, [?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Spivak. ?] And was rented to them because they lived next door.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They had their business.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they rented from us two rooms.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My brothers were home.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They lived-- my mother and three of us.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
